lead_paragraph: In conjunction with Red Bull, the organizers of the GHE20G0TH1K party held what was advertised as the final event in one of New York’s least predictable night-life institutions.

headline.print_headline: A Corporate Yet Subversive Party Says It’s Flicking on the Lights
headline.main: Review: The GHE20G0TH1K Party Says It Is Flicking On the Lights

snippet: In conjunction with Red Bull, the organizers of the GHE20G0TH1K party held what was advertised as the final event in one of New York’s least predictable night-life institutions.
abstract: Jon Caramanica reviews performances at dance party GHE20G0TH1K, presented by Red Bull Music Academy, at Brooklyn Night Bazaar.
